pageContext.claim: “Why didn't the I.G., who spent 8 years with the Obama Administration (Did she Report on the failed H1N1 Swine Flu debacle where 17,000 people died?), want to talk to the Admirals, Generals, V.P. & others in charge, before doing her report. Another Fake Dossier!”
pageContext.analysis: There is no reason to believe that Christi Grimm’s report is false. She served presidents of both parties and the IG’s office in the Department of Health and Human Services did write reports about the H1N1 response — where the estimated death toll during the H1N1 epidemic was 12,469.
